   J2ME is defined as "Java 2 Platform, Micro Edition (J2ME)".  Popular with mobile or embedded devices.  See this link for lots of detail.  [http://java.sun.com/j2me/ Sun's Developer network page].
<P>
   J2ME is designed to be lightweight, only link in code that is absolutely necessary.  So that J2ME app will have the smallest memory & CPU footprint possible.  You can see where this is a requirement in low speed CPU, battery powered devices like cell phones.
